ZorkMUD Version

This version of Zork is a port of the original source code, preserved by
MITDDC at:

  https://github.com/MITDDC/zork

The game has been ported to the LDMud driver, written in LPC, and runs on
a slimmed down version of Darkwind.

If you like what you see, come visit us at Darkwind:

  https://play.darkwind.ai
